| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2253 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0e4b2f93-60d4-5c58-a69b-74883605ccb6"
